# API Docker build uses repo root as context (apps/api/Dockerfile.production).
# Keep this tight so `fly deploy` / CI uploads stay small.

**/.git
**/.github
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.next
**/coverage
**/*.log

# Apps not needed for API image
apps/web
apps/browser-worker

docs
e2e
playwright-report
test-results

*.md
!README.md

.env
.env.*
!.env.example
